detailsSection:
The Microsoft Windows Server Print Server Management Pack monitors the performance and availability of print servers. In addition to monitoring the health of print servers, the management pack can also provide insight into the status of shared printers. By detecting, alerting on, and automatically responding to critical events and performance indicators, this management pack helps indicate, correct, and prevent possible operating system service outages.

Feature Summary
The management pack provides functionality to:
  • Monitor performance and Windows events
  • Display detailed monitoring data through views
  • Allow operator to manage print servers
  • Ensure correct configurations
